WEBVTT

00:00.150 --> 00:04.198
Etihad Airways have today unveiled new product and service offerings...

00:04.604 --> 00:07.425
...with a completely reimagined approach to air travel.

00:07.995 --> 00:08.858
The Residence,...

00:09.239 --> 00:11.352
...the only three-room cabin in the sky,...

00:11.861 --> 00:15.420
...features a living room, separate double bedroom and en suite shower room...

00:15.647 --> 00:17.382
...plus a personal butler.

00:18.767 --> 00:20.601
The A380 First Apartment.

00:21.062 --> 00:24.181
It's a fully private suite with separate reclining lounge seat,...

00:24.577 --> 00:28.385
...full-length bed, personal vanity unit, wardrobe and minibar.

00:29.975 --> 00:35.080
The Boeing 787 First Suite has a 26-inch-wide Poltrona Frau seat...

00:35.196 --> 00:39.414
...that converts to a comfortable 80.5-inch fully flat bed.

00:40.057 --> 00:44.900
The Business Class Studio, available on both the A380 and Boeing 787,...

00:45.346 --> 00:48.397
...has a luxurious standard that you usually find in first class...

00:48.498 --> 00:49.769
...for the rest of the industry.

00:51.258 --> 00:53.351
Economy class is also new.

00:53.850 --> 00:55.259
It's an ergonomic seat,...

00:55.411 --> 00:58.288
...a smart seat design with fixed-wing headrest.

00:59.619 --> 01:03.987
The lobby aboard the A380 is a communal area where guests can gather,...

01:04.096 --> 01:07.111
...mingle and enjoy Etihad's world-class service.

